Some of the structures in the &quot;Petra Archaeological Park&quot; where spatially documented by the [[Zamani Project]] and are visible on the maDIH repository.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|title=The Zamani Project, Petra, Jordan (مشروع زماني، البترا) - MaDiH (مديح)|url=https://madih-data.kdl.kcl.ac.uk/dataset/the-zamani-project-petra-jordan|access-date=2020-07-09|website=madih-data.kdl.kcl.ac.uk|language=en}}&lt;/ref&gt;

